text:
I've always had a thing for package design. It can really make the most basic products feel elevated, or add a bit of surprise and delight to the experience. This is nothing new, but I enjoyed this little post:
<https://www.wired.com/2016/11/9-boring-objects-come-pretty-packages/>

attachments.title: 9 Very Boring Objects That Come in Very Pretty Packages
attachments.text: No, really. These objects are boring as hell. But the packages? OMG
